  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Evaluation the amount of bone height gained when using titanium mesh in closing the lateral
      window of the sinus compared to collagen membrane.Evaluation the quality of new bone gained
      when using of the titanium mesh to close the lateral window of the maxillary sinus as a new
      option for tenting compared to collagen membrane.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      this study is aimed to review the bone height, quality and closure of lateral osteotomy used
      for maxillary sinus floor lifting comparing titanium mesh to collagen membrane.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
