  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  no signs of sinus pathology non or light smokers less than 20 cigarettes per day no
             systemic disease that may affect normal healing no pscychiatric problems no history of
             neoplasms or radiation therapy to the head and neck no previous bone augmentation to
             implant site

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Sinus pathology. Heavy smokers more than 20 cigarettes per day Patients with systemic
             disease that may affect normal healing. Psychiatric problems Disorders to implant are
             related to history of radiation therapy to the head and neck neoplasia, or bone
             augmentation to implant site.
      </textblock>
